@orderonline
Feature: Order Dominos Pizza Online
  We want to step through a simple scenario for training
 
@location
Scenario: Order Multiple Pizzas
  Given I visit the Dominos home page
  When I click the "Order Online" tab
  Then I should see the Dominos Location Search page
  Given I see the Dominos Location Search page
  Then I should see the address information page
  When I see the address information page I should enter my address
  Given I have entered information in to the fields for address information
  Then I can select items to order
  When I have completed my order I should be able to select multiple items 

